# {{.Name}}

{{.Description}}

This directory is an [**oz workspace**](https://github.com/oz-tools/oz): a small, explicit convention for LLM-first development — agents, specs, a trust hierarchy, and a single **`oz` CLI** for validation, structural graphs, audits, and optional MCP.

**Standard version:** `OZ.md` declares **oz standard v{{.OZVersion}}**.

## Prerequisites

- The [**oz**](https://github.com/oz-tools/oz) binary on your `PATH` (install from this repository’s `code/oz` with `go install` / `make`, or use a released build when available).

## First steps

1. Open **[`AGENTS.md`](./AGENTS.md)** — workspace entry for people and models; pick a role and follow that agent’s read-chain.
2. Run **`oz validate`** from any path under the workspace root (oz discovers the root automatically).
3. When you need routing, drift checks, or audits against the repo tree, run **`oz context build`** first (writes gitignored `context/graph.json`).

